Properties.EnglishScriptText: [[She was brilliant!]] I thought she was brilliant. Can't believe you introduced me to her.
[[She made me nervous.]] Honestly, she was a bit intimidating.
[[That sounds suspicious.]] That does seem strange. Sounds as if they're planning something.
[[That hardly sounds incriminating.]] You may be reading into it. Talking to people isn't a crime.
[[Would be good to investigate.]] I think that's a fine idea. Information is power.
[[I wouldn't. Poachers are dangerous.]] I'm not sure that's such a good idea. The poachers seem a dangerous lot.
